Subject: [PATCH] docs: fix documentation inconsistencies
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Fix outdated mocha/chai test examples in Quickstart-on-how-to-write-tests.md
  to use vitest patterns (VitestTestContext, arrow function beforeEach, vitest
  imports instead of chai/mocha)
- Fix incorrect pnpm install command in Generate-code-from-TypeSpec.md
  ('npm install -g @pnpm' → 'npm install -g pnpm')
- Fix missing trailing '...' in pnpm build --filter commands in
  steps-after-generations.md (Windows and Linux playback/record examples)
- Update using-azure-identity.md:
  - InteractiveBrowserCredential: replace deprecated implicit grant flow
    description with current authorization code + PKCE flow, add Node.js
    support info, remove stale browser-only note
  - DefaultAzureCredential: update credential chain to include
    WorkloadIdentityCredential, VisualStudioCodeCredential, AzureCliCredential,
    AzurePowerShellCredential, and AzureDeveloperCliCredential

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
